After a long time found something this addictive and worthy of listening over and over. It is
really rare to find new art this compelling now a days. Past three weeks I have been listening to this during my drives from office to home…..and intentionally
not calling people so I could listen to this (yes time is very rare commodity in New York City life, if it was a commodity). THANK YOU Pak Coke Studio for such a priceless rendition of two great voices. #LuvAbida4G8gift2EngineeringAudiance                                             #RahatHighPitchNotesToughCurvesWithgr8Control. #LoveFromNYC
